      "title": "Permanence and positive periodic solution for the single-species nonautonomous delay diffusive models",
      "abstract": "Abstract Single-species nonautonomous delay diffusion models with nonlinear growth rates are investigated. Some sufficient conditions are determined that guarantee the permanence of the species and the existence of a positive periodic solution which is global attractively."
